title: The Johnny Red Eyes (Discography) (2013)(SmileymanXD)
description:
As part of my on-going quest for good music hidden in the furthest reaches of the deep net, I bring you: The Johnny Red Eyes.

One of the only bands to be still active on my list, these Toronto noise-punk/ska outfit kick ass and take names, even if their ep's need a bit of a remastering.

This torrent includes their two EP's:
2011's No Pie (released in 2013, because they can) - A nice ska release for stoners.
2012's Planet Danger - A noisey rock filled release
(word on the street is this have a full length coming soon - a lot heavier and experimental)

I own both of these releases and have expressed permission from the band to post this torrent.

Check the band out here: <a href="
http://thejohnnyredeyes.tumblr.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thejohnnyredeyes.tumblr.com/</a>

ENJOY AND SEED!!!
